  * getCurrentSequenceNumber() - returns max sequence number
- Created TaskSessionRepository interface and implementation
  * findById() - direct SQL query by session ID
  * findByImRoute() - uses idx_session_im_route index
  * findByParentId() - uses idx_session_parent index
  * findByStatus() - filters by status
  * saveSession() - submits InsertTaskSessionEvent
